data.description: Sitting on just under a half-acre of land, this home has so much charm and character! 3 Bedroom / 3 Bath Split Floor Plan home in the Weatherstone subdivision of Bessemer/McCalla area is just stunning! The home features beautiful crown molding and hardwood flooring. Eat-in Kitchen boasts granite countertops, breakfast bar with plenty of cabinets. The Great Room with its high, vaulted ceiling and gas log Fireplace w/ tv inset, opens out onto the new deck overlooking the expansive back yard. The Split Bedroom floor plan offers lots of privacy. The Master Suite features a trayed-ceiling and Master Bath with Dual Vanities, Jetted, Garden Tub, Separate Shower and water closet plus a large Walk-in Closet. Laundry Room is on the main level just off the kitchen. Your family will enjoy the huge Bonus room in the Basement that could easily convert to a 4th Bedroom suite as it has a full bath and sitting area. Too many features to fully convey here - you must see it for yourself!
